Package com.google.gwt.typedarrays.shared

Interface Uint8ClampedArray

All Superinterfaces:
ArrayBufferView, Uint8Array
All Known Implementing Classes:
Uint8ArrayNative, Uint8ClampedArrayImpl, Uint8ClampedArrayNativeEmul
public interface Uint8ClampedArray extends Uint8Array
A view representing an ArrayBuffer as 8-bit unsigned integers. Storing out-of-range values are mapped to valid values by clamping to the range 0-255.
invalid @link 
{@link "http://www.khronos.org/registry/typedarray/specs/latest/#7"
